<hymn_number>6074</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yạ ʿjybạaⁿ fy mḥbth ạlʿẓymẗ (yạ msyḥy)2
 qd ḥmlt ạlạ̹tẖm ʿn nfsy ạlạ̉tẖymẗ (tfdy rwḥy)2
 ạlqrạr- yạ ʿjybạaⁿ msẖyrạaⁿ ạ̹lhạ qdyrạaⁿ yạ ạ̉bạ ạ̉bdyạaⁿ yạ rỷys ạlslạm yạ yswʿ
 2- yạ qwyạaⁿ qd gẖlbt ạlqbr wạlmwt (ḥyn qmt)2
 bl sḥqt ạlṣl wạlạ̉ʿdạʾ ạ̉sẖhrt (wạntṣrt)2
 3- yạ ḥbyby ḥbk yḥlw lrwḥy (fhw nwry)2
 bl sẖfạʾ wdwạʾ ljrwḥy (wsrwry)</lyrics>
<title>yạ ʿjybạ msẖyrạ</title>
</song>